////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
// Assigning a AXI4+ATOP interface to a monitor modport, as if you would do `assign mon = axi_if;`
//
// The channel assignment `AXI_ASSIGN_MONITOR(mon_dv, axi_if)` assigns all signals from `axi_if`
// to the `mon_dv` interface.
